#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:2
msgid "Aerospike"
msgstr "Aerospike"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:4
msgid ""
"An L2 adapter backed by the native C++ Aerospike connector (the same "
"``ConnectorBase`` worker-pool harness used by ``fs_native``), wrapped "
"with ``NativeConnectorL2Adapter``.  KV objects are stored under a meta "
"record plus optional payload segments so values larger than the server "
"record cap are transparently sharded."
msgstr "一个由原生 C++ Aerospike 连接器支持的 L2 适配器（与 ``fs_native`` 使用的相同 ``ConnectorBase`` 工作池框架），由 ``NativeConnectorL2Adapter`` 封装。KV 对象存储在一个元记录下，加上可选的有效负载段，因此大于服务器记录上限的值会被透明地分片。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:10
msgid "**Prerequisites -- Building with Aerospike support:**"
msgstr "**前提条件 -- 使用 Aerospike 支持构建：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:12
msgid ""
"The Aerospike extension is **not** built by default.  Install the "
"Aerospike C client, then build with ``BUILD_AEROSPIKE=1`` (or set "
"``AEROSPIKE_INCLUDE_DIR``):"
msgstr "Aerospike 扩展**默认情况下**并未构建。安装 Aerospike C 客户端，然后使用 ``BUILD_AEROSPIKE=1`` 构建（或设置 ``AEROSPIKE_INCLUDE_DIR``）："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:19
msgid ""
"See :doc:`/developer_guide/extending_lmcache/native_connectors` (section "
"\"Built-in Aerospike backend\") for installing the C client into "
"``.deps/`` and the ``aerospike-client-c.env`` example."
msgstr "请参阅 :doc:`/developer_guide/extending_lmcache/native_connectors`（章节“内置 Aerospike 后端”）以了解如何将 C 客户端安装到 ``.deps/`` 以及 ``aerospike-client-c.env`` 示例。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:23
msgid "**Required fields:**"
msgstr "**必填字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:25
msgid "``hosts``: Seed hosts as ``host:port[,host:port...]``."
msgstr "``hosts``: 种子主机格式为 ``host:port[,host:port...]``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:27
msgid "**Optional fields:**"
msgstr "**可选字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:29
msgid ""
"``namespace`` (str, default ``\"lmcache\"``): Aerospike namespace.  Must "
"exist on the server and have ``nsup-period > 0`` if you rely on TTL "
"expiry."
msgstr "``namespace`` (str, default ``\"lmcache\"``): Aerospike 命名空间。必须在服务器上存在，并且如果依赖于 TTL 过期，则必须具有 ``nsup-period > 0``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:31
msgid ""
"``set_name`` / ``set`` (str, default ``\"kv_chunks\"``): Aerospike set "
"name."
msgstr "``set_name`` / ``set`` (str, default ``\"kv_chunks\"``): Aerospike 集合名称。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:32
msgid ""
"``num_workers`` (int, default ``8``, > 0): C++ worker threads for I/O.  "
"This is the real I/O queue depth -- raise it to push throughput."
msgstr "``num_workers`` (int, default ``8``, > 0): C++ 工作线程用于 I/O。这是真正的 I/O 队列深度——提高它以提升吞吐量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:34
msgid "``read_timeout_ms`` (int, default ``1000``): Client read timeout."
msgstr "``read_timeout_ms`` (int, default ``1000``): 客户端读取超时。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:35
msgid "``write_timeout_ms`` (int, default ``2000``): Client write timeout."
msgstr "``write_timeout_ms`` (int, default ``2000``): 客户端写入超时。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:36
msgid ""
"``default_ttl_seconds`` (int, default ``86400``): Record TTL.  ``0`` uses"
" the namespace default TTL."
msgstr "``default_ttl_seconds`` (int, default ``86400``): 记录的生存时间（TTL）。 ``0`` 使用命名空间的默认 TTL。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:38
msgid ""
"``target_segment_bytes`` (int, default ``0``): Target shard size.  ``0`` "
"uses the discovered server record cap."
msgstr "``target_segment_bytes`` (int, default ``0``): 目标分片大小。 ``0`` 使用发现的服务器记录上限。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:40
msgid ""
"``max_record_bytes`` (int, default ``0``): Override the server record "
"cap. ``0`` discovers it at construction time."
msgstr "``max_record_bytes`` (int, default ``0``): 覆盖服务器记录上限。 ``0`` 在构造时发现该上限。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:42
msgid ""
"``username`` / ``password`` (str, default ``\"\"``): Optional Enterprise "
"Edition authentication."
msgstr "``username`` / ``password`` (str, default ``\"\"``): 可选的企业版身份验证。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:44
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0``): Maximum L2 capacity in GB for"
" client-side usage tracking / eviction.  ``0`` disables tracking."
msgstr "``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0``): 用于客户端使用跟踪/逐出的最大 L2 容量（以 GB 为单位）。``0`` 禁用跟踪。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:47
msgid ""
"**Environment variable fallbacks.**  When the corresponding config value "
"is empty, these environment variables are used: "
"``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_HOSTS``, ``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_NAMESPACE``, "
"``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_SET``, ``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_USERNAME``, "
"``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_PASSWORD``."
msgstr "**环境变量回退。** 当相应的配置值为空时，将使用这些环境变量：``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_HOSTS``、``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_NAMESPACE``、``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_SET``、``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_USERNAME``、``LMCACHE_AEROSPIKE_PASSWORD``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/aerospike.rst:52
msgid "**Configuration examples:**"
msgstr "**配置示例：**"

